translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さあ、次だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright, next."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 先日、JAPANの陰陽にアレと似たものを見た。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The other day, I saw something similar to that in the yin and yang of JAPAN."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 専門家の所見が欲しいな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'd like an expert's opinion."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふぅん……こっちは孫からの話で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm... this is from a story my grandson told me,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 聖魔法をちょいと漁り直したい気になったね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "it makes me want to browse through some holy magic again."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「聖魔法……ネクロマンサーか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Holy magic... Necromancer, huh."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼスでは調べにくいな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's hard to investigate that in Zeth..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「その二つじゃ、だいぶ取りこぼしがあるようだよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Those two leave quite a few gaps, it seems."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こいつも専門知識がないと調べにくい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This one is also hard to investigate without specialized knowledge."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふん、ならば……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmph, if that's the case..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあああぁ……なんだか、すごかったですね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Haaaah... That was somehow amazing, wasn't it?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………元気な爺だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...What a lively old man."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うぅ……宿題どうしよう……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ugh... What should I do about my homework..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「人民よ……！　私は帰ってきた！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "People...! I have returned!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ネルソンが、ランス城の廊下を歩いていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nelson was walking down the corridor of Rance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ひそひそ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Whisper whisper...
"Hey... is that... ?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ……ネルソン・サーバー……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah... Nelson Sarver..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ペンタゴンっていうテロリスト……国の恥だよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The terrorist called Pentagon... he's a disgrace to the country."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんか……カルトなんだって？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I heard... he's part of some cult?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょっと怖い……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Kind of scary..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうよ……あの男のテロで、魔軍がやってきて……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's right... because of that man's terrorism, the demon army came..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼスじゃ、すっごくいっぱい人が死んだの
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In Zeth, a lot of people died.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なぜそんな者がこの城で……？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Why is someone like that in this castle...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さぁなぁ……マジノラインの攻防で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Who knows... during the defense of the Maginot Line,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何かあったらしいが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: something must have happened..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （そうだ……許してはいけない……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (That's right... I must not forgive...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 忘れても、いけない……私は……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I must not forget... I am...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背中に向けられる嫌悪と不信の視線を受け、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Receiving hateful and distrustful gazes directed at his back,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ネルソンは黙然と目を伏せる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nelson silently lowered his eyes.
"Hm?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「む…………おお、ランス君……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm... Oh, Lance-kun...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、総統殿……だったな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, it's the Supreme Commander... right?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おっさん…………誰だったか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Old man... who was he again?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: んーーー……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmmmmm..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……忘れた、のかね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Have you forgotten?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私はペンタゴンで、ゼスを崩壊させ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I was Pentagon, who destroyed Zeth...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一級市民も二級市民も……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: both first-class and second-class citizens...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おお、ペンタゴン。懐かしいな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh, Pentagon. That brings back memories."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お前んとこの接待で楽しんだことは覚えてるぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I remember enjoying myself at your hospitality.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの時のねーちゃん、また連れてこい。がははは」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Bring that girl from that time again. Hahaha!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは笑い声を上げながら去っていった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance laughed as he walked away.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ふっ。未来に生きるとは……ああいうことか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Hmph. To live in the future... I see that's what it means."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ネルソンが？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Nelson?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうなの。最近、いろんな部署の人たちと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yes. Recently, he's been gathering with people from various departments every night...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 夜な夜な、集会を開いてるみたいなの……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it seems like he holds meetings night after night..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「集会……ですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Meetings... you say?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: でも、ネルソンさん……城に来た時は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But when Nelson-san came to the castle,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: みんな良い顔してなかったような……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: everyone didn't seem happy..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「言いくるめちゃったみたい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It seems he talked them around.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう、だいぶいろんな人と打ち解けてて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He's already gotten friendly with a lot of people,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 集会もけっこうな数の人が集まってるみたいよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and quite a few people seem to be gathering at the meetings."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「言いくるめ……ってなぁ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Talked them around... that's something.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法じゃあるまいし」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's not like magic, after all."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いえ。話術……コミュニケーションの力は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No. Rhetoric... the power of communication is

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 侮れませんよ。特に、あのネルソンさんは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: not to be underestimated. Especially since that Nelson-san

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 高いレベルで持ってるようですし」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: seems to possess it at a high level."
